flowchart LR
    F["(1) Complex FFT frame<br/>In: ADC/FFT cube<br/>Out: frame[t,rx,chirp/bin]"]
    P["(2) Preprocess frame<br/>In: complex frame<br/>Out: clutter-reduced profile + spectral history"]
    D["(3) Detect candidate bins<br/>In: preprocessed profile<br/>Out: candidate points (range/xyz/zone/conf)"]
    T["(4) Track best target over time<br/>In: candidates + previous track<br/>Out: tracked target (stable xyz/bin/vz/conf)"]
    V["(5) Extract vital micro-features<br/>In: spectral history + tracked bin<br/>Out: micro-state + periodicity features"]
    A["(6) Estimate activity<br/>In: tracked target + micro-state + motion_level<br/>Out: occupancy + posture + motion_score"]
    RX["(7) Extract respiration signal<br/>In: tracked bin + spectral history<br/>Out: live_signal + derivative + quality"]
    RA["(8) Analyze respiration metrics<br/>In: respiration signal<br/>Out: RR + apnea + cycle metrics"]
    O["(9) Emit unified EngineOutput<br/>In: track + activity + respiration branches<br/>Out: typed EngineOutput"]

    F --> P --> D --> T
    T --> V --> O
    T --> A --> O
    T --> RX --> RA --> O
    N1["Preprocess gate: downstream is blocked until warmup_frames calibration completes."]:::note
    N2["Detection formula (concept): candidate if magnitude(bin) > threshold and zone is valid."]:::note
    N3["Tracking gate: only confirmed/stable continuity feeds activity and respiration."]:::note
    N4["Respiration gate: requires spectral history and confirmed bin lock."]:::note
    N5["Motion formula: motion_score = clamp(motion_level / restless_max, 0, 1)."]:::note
    P -.-> N1
    D -.-> N2
    T -.-> N3
    RX -.-> N4
    A -.-> N5

    classDef stage fill:#F8FAFC,stroke:#475569,color:#0F172A;
    classDef output fill:#FEF3C7,stroke:#F59E0B,color:#78350F;
    classDef note fill:#FFFBEB,stroke:#D97706,color:#7C2D12,stroke-dasharray: 4 3;
    class F,P,D,T,V,A,RX,RA stage;
    class O output;
